<p>With a glass of wine in hand, Sebastian sat on his couch and reacted hilariously to some of the episode's most iconic moments and characters. </p>

<p>He kept the camera fixed on his face with the sound of the Gossip Girl pilot's opening scene playing in background before uttering: '"Episode one!'</p>

