<p>In the scene, Chace sported his character's signature coif as he and actress Blake Lively, who played the series' main character Serena van der Woodsen, engaged in some tense back-and-forth.</p>

<p>With Serena having just rejected Nate's affections, Sebastian turned his camera away from the television screen so he could share his reaction with his online following. </p>

